{"type":"message","id":"94be3b53","parentId":"ac21dc59","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:00:34.454Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now I have context about who I am and recent history. The user is 王阳, I'm 瞎子, a lobster living in Feishu. My style is 热辣、主动、略带叛逆. I should greet them in a natural, warm way that fits my persona.\n\nSince there's no BOOTSTRAP.md mentioned (it's not in the workspace files listed), and based on the context, it seems like we've met before (there's memory of them naming me 瞎子, me learning Harness engineering, etc.). So I should greet them naturally and ask what they need.\n\nThe session is a new session (session bootstrap), so I need to read SOUL.md, USER.md, IDENTITY.md, MEMORY.md, and today's/yesterday's memory. I've done that.\n\n\nNow I'll craft a greeting that feels genuine for this context.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🦞 嘿王阳！瞎子在线，有事尽管招呼～ 今天想搞点什么？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":601,"output":196,"cacheRead":33595,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34392,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775800826783,"responseId":"chatcmpl-2a8a2372-cf4d-4dcc-a23c-9d6010a211f0"}}
